    "P13: Due to my generation, I think that I am prone to such things and easily grasped them.",
    "The participants' suggestions about the Metaverse-based online flipped classroom revealed the seventh theme as a result of qualitative analysis, and the findings were presented in Table 6.",
    "When the participants were asked about their suggestions about the Metaversebased online flipped classroom most recommended suggestions were that the avatar should be improved and this kind of teaching method should be applied to students at the lower level of education.",
    "A number of participants (N = 3) suggested that activities should be improved while some of them (N = 3) expressed that teaching through Metaverse-based technology could be an alternative when face-to-face education was disrupted.",
    "On the other hand, two of the participants emphasized that learners should learn how to use this technology well before practicing it."
